---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const canonicalURL = new URL('/igi-certificate/', Astro.site).toString();
const deCounterpart = new URL('/labordiamanten/igi-zertifikat/', Astro.site).toString();
---

<Layout
  title="IGI Certificate for Lab Grown Diamonds"
  description="What is an IGI certificate for lab grown diamonds? Learn what the report includes and why it matters when buying diamonds in Germany."
  canonicalURL={canonicalURL}
  ogLocale="en_US"
  schema="article"
  alternates={[
    { hreflang: 'de-DE', href: deCounterpart },
    { hreflang: 'en', href: canonicalURL },
    { hreflang: 'x-default', href: deCounterpart },
  ]}
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', item: new URL('/', Astro.site).toString() },
    { name: 'IGI Certificate', item: canonicalURL },
  ]}
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-600">English guide</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 break-words text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-gray-950 sm:text-4xl">IGI Certificate for Lab Grown Diamonds</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
      The International Gemological Institute is one of the most common grading laboratories for lab grown diamonds.
      Its reports help buyers compare stones using transparent quality data.
    </p>

    <div class="content-flow mt-10">
      <h2>What an IGI report includes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Confirmation that the stone is laboratory-grown</li>
        <li>Growth method, such as CVD or HPHT</li>
        <li>Cut, colour, clarity and carat weight</li>
        <li>Polish, symmetry, fluorescence and measurements</li>
        <li>A unique report number for verification</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why it matters</h2>
      <p>
        A certificate makes pricing and quality easier to compare. For German buyers and jewellers, IGI documentation
        provides confidence that the stone matches the stated specifications.
      </p>

      <p>
        For German details, see the <a href="/labordiamanten/igi-zertifikat/" class="font-medium text-gold-600 underline">IGI-Zertifikat guide</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
